# Ignore .claude/ contents EXCEPT versioned artifacts (task plans).
# Using .claude/* rather than .claude/ so git still descends into the
# directory and the negation below can re-include specific subpaths.
.claude/*
# Keep task plans version-controlled so multi-session / multi-machine
# workflows can resume from them.
!.claude/tasks/
# Same for §10 handoff plans — track them so worktree removal doesn't lose
# the decision record (see CLAUDE.md "plan 버전관리").
!.claude/plans/

### Worktrees ###
.worktrees/
